text = "The astronomy room is full of patterns, dates, and distant clues.\n\nLook carefully at what hangs on the walls and what rests on the desk.\n\nThe room will not give you its answer all at once. You will need to connect the pieces.\n\nStay patient. The sky only makes sense when you read it in the right order."
